V0016_01_00_00_0.text: Allow me to teach you that experience outweighs youth.

V0016_01_00_01_0.text: It's never wise to underestimate your elders!

V0016_01_00_02_0.text:
Ho ho!
There's nothing more fun than a great game!

V0016_01_00_03_0.text: There's still plenty of life in these bones!

V0016_01_00_04_0.text:
Beware, Yugi.
I'm up-to-date with the latest strategies.

V0016_01_00_05_0.text:
Hello Téa!
Grown into a Duelist, have you?

V0016_01_00_06_0.text:
Yugi...
I will win this Duel...

V0016_01_00_07_0.text: I wonder what insects are in your deck, Weevil.

V0016_03_00_00_0.text: Just because I'm older doesn't mean I can't Duel.

V0016_03_00_01_0.text:
Ho ho!
This comes from years of experience!

V0016_03_00_05_0.text:
Ho ho!
You're playing really well!

V0016_05_00_00_0.text:
My deck has the best card in the game.
If I draw it, I win!

V0016_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I set!

V0016_07_13_00_0.text: I'm going to set the Pendulum Scale!

V0016_11_01_00_0.text: I'm Summoning a monster in Defense Position!

V0016_20_00_01_0.text: I'm going to Set a card.

V0016_21_00_01_0.text: If you don't do something, I'm going to win.

V0016_21_00_03_0.text:
Ho ho.
I end my turn.

V0016_21_00_05_1.text: In all my years, I've never been in this much trouble!

V0016_28_00_00_0.text:
Ho ho ho!
I can't let you kids defeat me yet!

V0016_28_00_01_0.text: I was quite skilled back in my day - and I still got it!

V0016_28_00_02_0.text:
Ho ho ho!
You Dueled well, my child.

V0016_28_00_03_0.text: The key to this game is to cherish every one of your cards.

V0016_28_00_04_0.text:
A Duelist must never lose hope.
Or their integrity.

V0016_28_00_05_0.text:
What's wrong, Yugi?
This isn't like you.

V0016_28_00_06_0.text:
Yugi, a card is like a puzzle piece.
Each one is important.

V0016_28_00_07_0.text: The one who assembles the Puzzle will constantly be tested.

V0016_28_00_07_1.text: You must not break - no matter what.

V0016_28_00_08_0.text: You've become quite the Duelist, Joey.

V0016_28_00_08_1.text:
Yugi might need to watch his back!
Ho ho ho!

V0016_28_00_09_0.text: I guess Spell Cards are too difficult for you.

V0016_28_00_10_0.text: You carry hundreds of cards in your briefcase.

V0016_28_00_10_1.text: But you must learn to cherish each one.

V0016_29_00_00_0.text: Time is catching up with me...

V0016_29_00_02_0.text: The next generation is taking over the game.

V0016_29_00_03_0.text: I may have lost, but I still love my cards.

V0016_29_00_04_0.text:
May I have that card for my store?
Promise I won't sell it!

V0016_29_00_06_0.text: True strength comes from fighting through your fears.

V0016_29_00_07_0.text: You played your Trap Cards like an expert!

V0016_29_00_08_0.text: I hope that you and Yugi are friends forever.

V0016_29_00_09_0.text: It frightens me that you would do anything to win...

V0016_29_00_10_0.text: He knew every move I was going to make!

V0016_33_00_00_0.text: Ho ho! Of course I intend to win!

V0016_33_00_01_0.text: I'll give you a tiny peek of what I can do!

V0016_33_00_02_0.text: Nothing in the world is useless.

V0016_34_00_00_0.text:
Are my eyes deceiving me?
That's a legendary rare card!

V0016_34_00_01_0.text: You've grown so much since I've last seen you.

V0016_34_00_02_0.text: Your heart contains a treasure that no money can buy.

V0016_34_00_03_0.text: How were you able to acquire such a rare card?

V0016_34_00_04_0.text: I've heard rumors about that card, but I've never seen it!

V0016_34_00_05_0.text: Oh no! I left that card in Defense Position!

V0016_34_00_06_0.text: There are benefits to being older and wise.

V0016_34_00_07_0.text: I want that card for my collection!

V0016_34_00_08_0.text: Wow! It's like a real monster is attacking me!

V0016_34_00_09_0.text: As a fellow gaming enthusiast, it's my honor to play you.

V0016_34_00_10_0.text: I'm too old to risk it all.

V0016_34_00_11_0.text: That card is so powerful that they stopped making it!

V0016_35_00_01_0.text: You whippersnappers can't match my experience!

V0016_36_00_00_0.text: It's up to you how this Duel will end.

V0016_36_00_01_0.text: If you don't stay alert, we will lose!

V0016_36_00_05_0.text: You're the only one who can win this, Yugi!

V0016_08_00_00_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Mirage of Nightmare!

V0016_08_00_01_0.text: I'm activating Mirage of Nightmare's effect!

V0016_08_00_02_0.text:
Ho ho!
I activate my Spell Card!
Swords of Revealing Light!

V0016_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Emergency Provisions!

V0016_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0016_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Monster Reborn!

V0016_08_00_06_0.text: I can activate this card when Blue-Eyes is on my field.

V0016_08_00_07_0.text: I activate my Continuous Spell, Spiral Spear Strike!

V0016_08_00_08_0.text:
Ho ho!
I'm activating Spiral Spear Strike's effect!

V0016_08_00_09_0.text:
I'll use my Equip Spell!
Horn of the Unicorn!

V0016_08_00_10_0.text: Horn of the Unicorn's effect activates!

V0016_08_00_11_0.text: I'm activating the Spell Card, De-Spell!

V0016_08_00_12_0.text: I'll activate the Spell Card, Remove Trap!

V0016_08_00_13_0.text: I'm activating the Quick-Play Spell, Mystical Space Typhoon!

V0016_08_00_14_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Card Trader!

V0016_08_00_15_0.text:
Ho ho!
I'll use Card Trader's effect!

V0016_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Obliterate!!!!

V0016_08_00_18_0.text: Obliterate!!! activates when it goes to the Graveyard!

V0016_08_00_19_0.text:
Ho ho!
I activate my Spell Card!
Contract with Exodia!

V0016_08_00_20_0.text:
Let me peek at your cards.
I activate The Eye of Truth!

V0016_08_00_21_0.text:
The Eye of Truth's effect activates.
Aren't you lucky.

V0016_08_00_22_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Ordeal of a Traveler!

V0016_08_00_23_0.text:
Ordeal of a Traveler activates!
Will you choose correctly?

V0016_08_00_24_0.text:
I'll activate my Trap!
Non Aggression Area!

V0016_08_00_25_0.text: I'll use this to regain my LP!

V0016_08_00_25_1.text: The Trap Card, Gift of The Mystical Elf!

V0016_09_00_01_0.text: Exodia, the Legendary Defender destroyed a DARK Fiend!

V0016_09_00_02_0.text: The Legendary Exodia Incarnate activates its effect!

V0016_09_00_03_0.text: The Legendary Exodia Incarnate activates when it's gone!

V0016_09_00_04_0.text: Exodia Necross activates its effect and gains ATK!

V0016_09_00_05_0.text: True Exodia and four of his limbs are on the field.

V0016_09_00_06_0.text: Due to Exodius's effect, I send a monster to the Graveyard.

V0016_09_00_07_0.text: All Forbidden One cards are in my Graveyard, so I win!

V0016_09_00_08_0.text: Due to Exxod, Master of The Guard's effect, you take damage!

V0016_09_00_09_0.text: Sangan's effect activates when it goes to the Graveyard!

V0016_09_00_10_0.text:
Ho ho!
Wandering Mummy's effect activates!

V0016_09_00_11_0.text:
Sinister Serpent's effect activates!
It returns to my hand!

V0016_09_00_12_0.text: Gambler of Legend activates his effect!

V0016_09_00_13_0.text: I see that Witch of the Black Forest went to the Graveyard!

V0016_13_00_00_0.text: I'm so happy that I can play this card again!

V0016_13_00_01_0.text: If I bring this card out, I'll win!

V0016_13_00_03_0.text: Right Leg of the Forbidden One!

V0016_13_00_04_0.text: Right Arm of the Forbidden One!

V0016_13_00_05_0.text: Left Leg of the Forbidden One!

V0016_13_00_06_0.text: Left Arm of the Forbidden One!

V0016_37_00_00_0.text: Exodia, the Legendary Defender can quell an army on its own!

V0016_13_00_07_0.text:
Come here!
Exodia, the Legendary Defender!

V0016_37_00_01_0.text: Free yourself from your shackles and release your power!

V0016_13_00_09_0.text:
Abide by your contract!
Exodia Necross!

V0016_13_00_11_0.text:
Step forth!
Exodius the Ultimate Forbidden Lord!

V0016_13_00_12_0.text:
Come out!
Exxod, Master of The Guard!

V0016_13_00_13_0.text: The ultimate magical knight rides into battle!

V0016_13_00_14_0.text: This is the legendary Fusion Monster!

V0016_13_00_15_0.text: Here comes one of the greatest Dragons!

V0016_13_00_17_1.text: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #1!

V0016_13_00_29_0.text: This card is one of the rarest Fiends.

V0016_13_00_30_0.text:
Ho ho!
This card reminds me of my younger days!

V0016_19_00_01_0.text:
This will have to do...
Exodia the Forbidden One! Attack!

V0016_19_00_02_0.text:
I guess I'll attack...
Go, Right Leg of the Forbidden One!

V0016_19_00_03_0.text:
Sigh...
I attack with Right Arm of the Forbidden One!

V0016_19_00_04_0.text:
Hmm...
Attack, Left Leg of the Forbidden One!

V0016_19_00_05_0.text:
Left Arm of the Forbidden One...
Attack, I guess!

V0016_19_00_06_0.text:
Exodia, the Legendary Defender!
Incinerate all your enemies!

V0016_19_00_07_0.text:
The Legendary Exodia Incarnate!
Scorch your foes!

V0016_19_00_08_0.text:
The Legendary Exodia Incarnate!
Stoke your fire and attack!

V0016_19_00_11_0.text: Attack, Exodius the Ultimate Forbidden Lord!

V0016_19_00_12_0.text:
Exxod, Master of The Guard!
Attack!

V0016_19_00_17_0.text: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #1 attacks!

V0016_19_00_30_0.text: Gambler of Legend is going to attack!

V0016_19_00_32_0.text: Witch of the Black Forest! Attack!
